# Aliases List

List all aliases in a project.

GET

/

aliases

Aliases List
    
    
    curl --request GET \
      --url https://api.example.com/aliases \
      --header 'Authorization: Basic <encoded-value>'
    
    
    {
      "aliases": [
        "<string>"
      ]
    }

